# Special instructions when generating Synapse
* Follow the best practices when generating Synapse artifacts.
* Always create a separate file for  endpoints.
* Always use call mediator instead of send mediator.
* Never use outSequence. It is DEPRECATED.

# Sample API Template without outSequence
```xml
<api xmlns="http://ws.apache.org/ns/synapse" name="name-here" context="context-here">
    <resource methods="GET" uri-template="">
        <inSequence>
        </inSequence>
    </resource>
</api>
```